# Hallucination Allowlist
#
# Each non-blank, non-comment line suppresses a specific finding.
# Format: <category>:<pattern>
#
# Categories:
#   dependency   - suppress fabricated-dependency warnings for a package name
#   import       - suppress phantom-import warnings for a module path
#   test         - suppress self-validating-test warnings for a file path glob
#
# IMPORTANT: Category-wide wildcards (e.g., dependency:*) are rejected.
# Patterns must be specific enough to target individual items.
# Changes to this file require CODEOWNERS approval.
#
# Examples:
#   dependency:my-internal-package
#   import:src/utils/internal-helper
#   test:tests/smoke/*.test.js
